name: PeachMixs
description:
My pixiv

More version on HuggingFace Model Card

My friend model here 😁

About

PeachMixs are various merge models base on a lot of different models. This version can generate good quality illustrations in low steps and have variety of content.

How to use:

  • VAE: anything you want use 😉( but I recommend kl f8 anime, OrangesMixs VAE (NAI VAE) and sd-vae-ft-mse)

  • Prompt: As simple as good.

  • Negative prompt: (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (monochrome:1.1), (bad_prompt_Version2:0.8)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Steps: DDIM 50～ , SDE Karass 20～

  • Clipskip: 1 (you can try 2)

  • Upscaler : Latent (nearest-exact)

  • CFG Scale : 5 -7 is good (4～8)

  • Denoise strength: 0.5 maybe

Use model:

  1. AOM2 FP16

  2. Basil Mix

  3. AnidosMix

  4. DosMix

  5. Anything V4

  6. Anything V4.5

  7. Dalcefo

FAQ + other sample/model: Huggingface and pixiv ( will upload later ^_^).
